<br>
Jaraxalle this is not a hit on you, but it's merely some advice. You should be thinking about getting weapons that are within your means. At level 51, the warrior epics are not within your means. If you tried to fight Severilous you'd be stunned for the whole fight and I'd be surprised if you got a swing in.  Look for some nice weapons within you means and fight for them, stuff like Defiance and Lamentation. Or if you have some cash go to the bazaar and look for a Frostbringer or Crescent Blades of Luclin.<br>
<br>
In my mind the warrior epics take a solid team of people 55-60 to get, they are a little harder but they are well worth it. Getting the warrior epics is just a stepping stone to harder stuff. If you combine the red sword and Horrifying Visage on an MT, you can easily generate enough agro to MT a lot of big mobs.<br>
<br>
As far as doing each step, well you aren't going to succeed on the first try more than likely. But not succeeding is no reason to give up, it's a way you learn in this game. We didn't get to the Spiroc Island in PoA until our second raid to PoA. We didn't take the queen until our second try. Those two encounters are probably the toughest parts of the warrior epic. If you can gather a raid force, you can at least learn how to do them.<br>
<br>
There are plenty of warriors that never get their epics, they go on to get better weapons. But I am sure if you asked them, if they were given the opportunity to complete the epics, they might want to do it just for fun. Seeing the blue and red lightsabers is pretty cool in itself. At any rate, it's a nice thing the warrior epics aren't a given. Not to knock rangers, but their epics are almost a given, for them it's not if they will get their epics, it's really about when.<br>
<br>
The way I see it, I am glad the warrior epic is not easy. I like it that way because every warrior on the server isn't running around with them. It's a prestige item and definitely still an achievement, because there are still encounters that can't be 1-grouped.<br>
<br>
