I don't take offense, I know I'm a little low for getting my epic.  However, wouldn't it be nice to get something fixed before you get it?<br>
<br>
I mean I won't get my epic most likely, simply because of the lame cost involed in getting an inferior weapon.  Like Heimdall said I can get better weapons for cheaper.  I saw a fleshgrinder for 40k the other day, the green scale alone would be more than that let alone everything else.  <br>
<br>
Can't we make it something that is worth getting?  I don't really care if it's made harder or added onto.  Make it something that we can be proud of.  <br>
<br>
When I started this thread, I wanted to know what the warrior community wanted for an upgrade.  What would most people feel is a sufficient upgrade?  Thie thread was hijacked long ago with shouts of &quot;it will never happen&quot;, and &quot;non-warriors saying it doesn't need an upgrade&quot;.  I don't think there was one good suggestion for an upgrade.  One person did suggest right click true north, LOL.  <br>
