<br>
Red epics create much aggro.  Enough aggro that, that and a willsapper or that and a fleshgrinder can allow the bearer to outtaunt a BoC or SoD.  Not 100% of the time, but enough to make it noticible.  The only thing that makes the epics really iffy is the dmg/delay.  But with a good haste item (s) and enchanter speed, they are still great for grouping and tanking lower tier mobs.  By the time you get to the harder mobs that require getting more extensive aggro, you should have better.<br>
